You'll be spending the rest of the week creating your own Sinatra blog.
Your blog must:
-Have RESTful CRUD routes
-Login functionality (multiple authors is a plus)
-Some CSS styling



Some helpful resources:
Restular: http://www.restular.com/
HTML Forms: https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_forms.asp
CSS in Sinatra: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24153013/stylesheet-not-applying-to-sinatra-erb-views
BCrypt Documentation: https://github.com/codahale/bcrypt-ruby
Sample Sinatra MVC Skeleton (feel free to look for your own if you want): https://github.com/CodingCorpsMarin/simple-sinatra-mvc
